description: Decimal expansion of cube root of 9.
references: Horace S. Uhler, Many-figure approximations for cubic root of 2, cubic root of 3, cubic root of 4 and cubic root of 9 with chi 2 data, Scripta Math. 18, (1952). 173-176.
